data.title: DR. UKE SONGS WITH UKULELE CHORD DIAGRAMS
data.text:
2 Page Medleys-Standard (gcea) & Baritone (dgbe) Tunings

Add interest to your playing and performing, by playing medleys (more than 400), conveniently arranged on 2 pages.

Work in Progress

Song Categories

This is an ongoing project. I will be adding song categories, which will make it easier for you to find particular song genres. Sweet!
